Package org.gvsig.fmap.swing.toc Description

TODO: Remove this package and its contents when gvSIG fmap control project contains new API for TOC widget

This is a port of gvSIG 1.x new TOC API. Only Interfaces and Listeners are ported.

This is used to prepares the PortableViewTOC as will be used in (it supposed to be) a short future (gvSIG 2.1 ??)
